original_text: My brother put a knife in my head. This was just a few days after my father had died. and we were sitting shiva. And the reason the fight started He saw a rat out in the yard or – this was out in Coney Island – and he started talk about it. And my mother had just sat down to have a cup of coffee and I told him to cut it out. 'Course kids y'know, he don't hafta listen to me. So that's when I grabbed his arm and twisted it up behind him. When I let go his arm there was a knife on the table, he just picked it up and he let me have it. And ... I started bleeding – like a pig. And naturally first thing to do run to the doctor, and the doctor just says "Just about this much more," he says, "and you'd a been dead."
